## Installation

## from PyPi

In your environment of choice, use pip to install meeglet:

```bash
pip install meeglet
```

### from the sources

Please clone the software, consider installing the dependencies listed in the \`environment.yml.

Then do in your conda/mamba environment of choice:

``` bash
pip install -e .
```

